      <rules>
        <rule name="Cloak &amp; Dagger" id="a298-f0d1-418e-3dcb" hidden="false">
          <description>Duellists are adept at fighting using their billowing cloaks to swirl at an enemy distracting him and warding off blows.


The Duellist counts as using a shield in close combat.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
